### Youyu - Shops
### Run this file to validate public and authenticated shop endpoints.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@userToken = mock-1001-USER

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Public shop endpoints
# ------------------------------------------------------------

### Shop module skeleton
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shops/skeleton

###

### Public shop detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shops/4001

###

### Public shop detail - non-existent shop
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shops/99999

###

### Shop insight snapshot
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shops/4001/insight-snapshot

###

### Public shop review list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shops/4001/reviews?page=1&pageSize=10

###

### Public shop review summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shops/4001/review-summary

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Authenticated user shop endpoints
# ------------------------------------------------------------

###

### Get my shop
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shops/mine
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### Apply for a shop
### Note: seed users may already have a shop or pending application.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shops/applications
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "HTTP Test Campus Shop",
  "description": "A shop application created from the HTTP validation collection.",
  "coverUrl": "https://example.com/shop-cover.jpg",
  "announcement": "Open for campus pickup."
}

###

### Get my shop - missing auth
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shops/mine
